    <p>Goli earns the top spot by combining the four most evidence-backed metabolism-supporting ingredients in a single gummy: apple cider vinegar for blood sugar regulation, green tea extract for thermogenesis, B-vitamins for energy metabolism cofactors, and chromium picolinate for insulin sensitivity. The brand's 18,000+ reviews and B-Corp certification provide the trust and transparency that matter in a category plagued by overclaimed, underdosed products. The taste is genuinely excellent — Goli pioneered the ACV gummy format and remains the flavor benchmark.</p>

